WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.070
[Ambient sound]

2
00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:10.460
Zhang Peizan: Yes, I came back from walking the horses that day (turns to look at Qianjin). Just when I walked to the garden, I heard the young lady and her fiancé talking.

3
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.590
Zhang Peizan: She asked him to come to the garden in the middle of the night to get gold. Feelings of greed stirred in my heart at that moment.

4
00:00:16.790 --> 00:00:18.900
[Opera orchestra plays]

5
00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:29.000
♪ Chorus (singing): He said that he stole a hairpin because he was greedy for gold (Zhang steals a hairpin, leaves the room and waits outside the garden while Xuechen descends from the stairs and enters the garden), and quietly waited outside the garden for Xuechun. ♪

6
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:41.000
[Opera orchestra plays]

7
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:50.700
♪ (Zhang claps his hands three times and appears above the wall. Xuechun notices him and goes to open the gate). He clapped his hands three times so that the gate would open (Zhang and Xuechun enter the garden one after another, Xuechun closes the gate), and he could exchange the hairpin for money without any hindrance (Xuechun walks over to Zhang, who hides his face behind his long sleeve). ♪

8
00:00:50.700 --> 00:01:43.000
[Opera orchestra plays]

9
00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:46.800
Xuechun: (takes the hairpin from Zhang) Mr. Lin, you must not let my lady’s kindness go to waste (gives Zhang the bag of gold).

10
00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:48.900
Xuechun: It's getting late, please go back (Xuechun opens the gate for Zhang).

11
00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:53.000
[Opera orchestra plays]

12
00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:56.500
♪ Chorus (singing): (Zhang trips over the threshold) Flustered, legs trembling, he fell to the ground and ruined his plan. ♪

13
00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:57.600
Xuechun: Mr. Lin? (Zhang accidentally reveals his face to Xuechun)

14
00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:58.000
[Sound effect: Gasp]

15
00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.300
Chorus: Xuechun recognized who it was and shouted loudly.

16
00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:00.000
Xuechun: Ah, it’s you!

17
00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:05.800
Zhang Peizan: (holds Xuechun’s right arm and threatens her with a knife) Don't shout. If you shout, I will kill you (Xuechun pushes Zhang away and runs).

18
00:02:05.800 --> 00:02:11.000
♪ Chorus (singing): One mistake of his caused her soul to travel to the underworld (Zhang catches up with Xuechun and stabs her with his knife). ♪

19
00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Xuechun: Help!

20
00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.500
[Music stops]

21
00:02:15.500 --> 00:02:26.900
Zhang Peizan: I saw Lin coming over just when I managed to hide the knife and the gold. So, he became my scapegoat!